Tried this prawn noodles stall. Had the big portion@6.50. Generous serving with 5 decent size prawns. Taste consider nice n acceptable to me ( since different people different taste bud). Can Just try n decide.
Tried small all prawn noodles tonight @6, 5 event size prawns
Value for money and delicious zi char in the heartlands. Fish Maw soup is restaurant quality. Will return.
Quite a few stall serving good food. Have came here for meals a few times.

7/4/22
